e:[["$","title","0",{"children":"How to get ready for ISO Certification Audit | ISO Certification Audit in UAE | Wizms"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"ISO Certification Audit in UAE via a third-party consulting services  enables to get a wider and transparent picture of the general business operations. To"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"ISO auditing in UAE, ISO Auditor in UAE, ISO Certification Audit, ISO Certification Audit in UAE, ISO Audit in Dubai, best ISO certification consultant in UAE, ISO consultants in UAE, ISO Certification process, ISO Certification in Dubai, ISO"}],["$","meta","3",{"property":"og:title","content":"How to get ready for ISO Certification Audit | ISO Certification Audit in UAE | Wizms"}],["$","meta","4",{"property":"og:description","content":"ISO Certification Audit in UAE via a third-party consulting services  enables to get a wider and transparent picture of the general business operations. To"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://wizms.net/how-to-get-ready-for-iso-audit"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:type","content":"article"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"article:published_time","content":"2026-01-02T06:30:42+00:00"}],["$","meta","8",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary"}],["$","meta","9",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"How to get ready for ISO Certification Audit | ISO Certification Audit in UAE | Wizms"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"ISO Certification Audit in UAE via a third-party consulting services  enables to get a wider and transparent picture of the general business operations. To"}],["$","link","11",{"rel":"icon","href":"/favicon.ico"}],["$","$L22","12",{}]]
10:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"However, they can point out the non-conformance and provide a date for re-audit."}]
11:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"For the non-conformities analysis, the ISO auditor in UAE looks at policies, procedures, and gather evidence to verify their compliance with the ISO certification standard."}]
12:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Types of Non-Conformities"}]
13:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"During the ISO Certification Audit, the Non-Conformities can be broadly categorized into two"}]
14:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Major Non-Conformities"}]
15:["$","p","18",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Minor Non-Conformities."}]
16:["$","p","19",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Major Non-Conformities"}]
17:["$","p","20",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Major Non-Conformities are any breakdown or a flaw that are present in the management system and makes it skewed from the ISO Certification Standard requirements."}]
18:["$","p","21",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Due to the misalignment of policy manuals, outdated documentation and operating procedures in the workplace, etc., could lead to major non-conformities."}]
19:["$","p","22",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Minor Non- Conformities"}]
1a:["$","p","23",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"When the scope of the organization is deviated from the ISO Certification Standard requirements is minimal, then that is minor non-conformities."}]
1b:["$","p","24",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Any minor shifts or flaws from the recommended best practices of ISO Certification can be flagged and requested for correction during the ISO auditing in UAE and proceed with the ISO certification."}]
1c:["$","p","25",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The corrective actions must be taken within the agreed timeline and must be re-audited. Once all the changes are applied and compliance requirements are met, the ISO Certification body will issue the ISO certificate."}]
1d:["$","p","26",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The overall goal of the management is to make the required enhancements to the system and business processes in Dubai. The nonconformity assessment is a way of identifying any vulnerabilities that were present otherwise it will not be addressed during the internal ISO audit."}]
1e:["$","p","27",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO Auditing in UAE via a third-party consulting services in UAE enables to get a wider and transparent picture of the general business operations and workflows that may not be validated by internal staff."}]
1f:["$","p","28",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Hence, non-conformity assessment is a great way to fully benefit from the ISO Certification audit and enhance the overall QMS ISO 9001 and get the ISO Certification for the organization."}]
20:["$","p","29",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"To know more about ISO Certification Audit in UAE, talk to our expert ISO Consultants in UAE right away!"}]
